WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:18.000
The Tempest by William Shakespeare

00:18.000 --> 00:26.000
Copyright Black Cat Publishing

00:26.000 --> 00:37.000
Hello, my name is William Shakespeare. I was born in Stratford upon Avon in England on the 23rd of April 1564.

00:37.000 --> 00:46.000
I write plays, but I like to act too. In England, I'm very famous. All sorts of people come and see my plays.

00:46.000 --> 00:51.000
Hamlet, Macbeth, Romeo and Juliet. Maybe you know them.

00:51.000 --> 01:03.000
I am the king of Naples. I am the king's son. And I am the king's brother.

01:03.000 --> 01:09.000
I am the Duke of Milan. And I am Prospero's brother. I'm not a good man.

01:09.000 --> 01:18.000
I am a good old man. I am the king's friend. I am the real Duke of Milan. And I'm a magician.

01:19.000 --> 01:28.000
I'm Prospero's daughter. I am a monster. And I'm a magic spirit.

01:28.000 --> 01:42.000
I'm a butler. I work on the kingship. I'm a jester and I work on the kingship too.

01:43.000 --> 01:48.000
Part 1. The Real Duke of Milan

01:48.000 --> 01:59.000
Prospero is the real Duke of Milan. But he does not live in Milan. He lives on a small, lonely island with his beautiful young daughter, Miranda.

01:59.000 --> 02:12.000
Prospero doesn't want to live on this island, but he has no choice. His bad brother, Antonio, says he is the Duke of Milan, and Prospero cannot return to the city.

02:12.000 --> 02:23.000
Prospero and Miranda are not the only people on the Little Island. There is also a magic spirit called Ariel and a monster called Caliban.

02:24.000 --> 02:38.000
Prospero is now their master, and they are his slaves. Prospero is a magician. He is very clever, and he knows a lot about magic and spells from his books.

02:38.000 --> 02:50.000
Ariel helps Prospero with his magic. Alonso, Antonio, Alonso's son Ferdinand, Sebastian and Gonzalo are on the king's boat.

02:51.000 --> 03:00.000
Prospero decides to punish his brother, Antonio. He is going to send a big storm, a tempest.

03:03.000 --> 03:06.000
Part 1.

03:07.000 --> 03:16.000
That's the king of Naples. And that's the Duke of Milan. Hello, everybody. Hello, my friend.

03:16.000 --> 03:27.000
Excuse me. Yes? Yes. I'm the Duke of Milan, not him. He is my brother, my very bad brother.

03:27.000 --> 03:29.000
Oh? Oh.

03:31.000 --> 03:44.000
Sorry, brother. I am strong, and you are not. Now I am the Duke, and you are a poor man. Now I live in your castle, and you live on a small island.

03:45.000 --> 03:47.000
Hahah.

03:51.000 --> 03:58.000
Now my bad brother is the Duke, and I live on this small island with my daughter Miranda.

03:59.000 --> 04:07.000
Yes. 12 years on this small island, with my father and Caliban, and Ariel.

04:07.000 --> 04:09.000
Who is Caliban?

04:09.000 --> 04:11.000
Who is Ariel?

04:11.000 --> 04:13.000
They are my slaves.

04:13.000 --> 04:16.000
No, they are not, Father.

04:16.000 --> 04:18.000
Caliban is a monster.

04:18.000 --> 04:21.000
And Ariel is a magic spirit.

04:21.000 --> 04:23.000
Listen, Miranda.

04:23.000 --> 04:26.000
I want to punish my brother and the king.

04:26.000 --> 04:30.000
I want to do some magic.

04:30.000 --> 04:33.000
My father has a magic book.

04:33.000 --> 04:38.000
He reads his book every day and he does lots of magic.

04:38.000 --> 04:41.000
I want to make a storm.

04:41.000 --> 04:43.000
A tempest.

04:43.000 --> 04:47.000
I want to make a tempest to punish the duke.

04:47.000 --> 04:52.000
The next day, the king and the duke are in a boat.

04:52.000 --> 04:56.000
And Prospero makes a magic tempest.

05:03.000 --> 05:06.000
Ariel, be quiet.

05:06.000 --> 05:10.000
I want to listen to the television.

05:10.000 --> 05:13.000
Why? What program is it?

05:13.000 --> 05:15.000
Is it football?

05:15.000 --> 05:19.000
No, it's the weather forecast.

05:19.000 --> 05:23.000
I want to know the weather for tomorrow.

05:23.000 --> 05:26.000
Today is a beautiful day.

05:26.000 --> 05:28.000
I don't know.

05:28.000 --> 05:32.000
It's sunny, but it's windy too.

05:32.000 --> 05:36.000
Perhaps it will rain tomorrow.

05:36.000 --> 05:40.000
With a forecast starting now.

05:40.000 --> 05:43.000
Good evening and welcome to the weather forecast.

05:43.000 --> 05:46.000
There will be snow on the mountains tomorrow,

05:46.000 --> 05:49.000
but it will be sunny near the sea.

05:49.000 --> 05:52.000
It will be cloudy in the afternoon.

05:52.000 --> 05:56.000
The next day, stay at home because it will be very stormy.

05:56.000 --> 05:59.000
There will be a big tempest.

05:59.000 --> 06:03.000
Oh no, a big tempest tomorrow.

06:03.000 --> 06:05.000
What's a tempest?

06:05.000 --> 06:08.000
Don't you know, Caliban?

06:08.000 --> 06:14.000
A tempest is a big, big storm.

06:14.000 --> 06:19.000
Now listen to the conversation again.

06:19.000 --> 06:24.000
Ariel, be quiet.

06:24.000 --> 06:28.000
I want to listen to the television.

06:28.000 --> 06:31.000
Why? What program is it?

06:31.000 --> 06:33.000
Is it football?

06:33.000 --> 06:37.000
No, it's the weather forecast.

06:37.000 --> 06:41.000
I want to know the weather for tomorrow.

06:41.000 --> 06:44.000
Today is a beautiful day.

06:44.000 --> 06:50.000
I don't know. It's sunny, but it's windy too.

06:50.000 --> 06:53.000
Perhaps it will rain tomorrow.

06:53.000 --> 06:57.000
With a forecast starting now.

06:57.000 --> 07:00.000
Good evening and welcome to the weather forecast.

07:00.000 --> 07:03.000
There will be snow on the mountains tomorrow,

07:03.000 --> 07:06.000
but it will be sunny near the sea.

07:06.000 --> 07:09.000
It will be cloudy in the afternoon.

07:09.000 --> 07:14.000
The next day, stay at home because it will be very stormy.

07:14.000 --> 07:16.000
There will be a big tempest.

07:16.000 --> 07:21.000
Oh no, a big tempest tomorrow.

07:21.000 --> 07:23.000
