07:23.000 --> 07:26.000
Don't you know, Caliban?

07:26.000 --> 07:36.000
A tempest is a big, big storm.

07:36.000 --> 07:43.000
Part two, the men are at sea when a big storm begins.

07:43.000 --> 07:45.000
The wind is blowing hard,

07:45.000 --> 07:49.000
and the big waves almost go over the top of the boat.

07:49.000 --> 07:52.000
The men are all very afraid.

07:52.000 --> 07:55.000
A man is steering the boat.

07:55.000 --> 07:58.000
He tries to stop it from going under the waves,

07:58.000 --> 08:00.000
but it is impossible.

08:00.000 --> 08:02.000
They start shouting for help.

08:02.000 --> 08:06.000
They must leave the ship to save themselves.

08:06.000 --> 08:09.000
There is a small island not too far away.

08:09.000 --> 08:11.000
The men don't know this,

08:11.000 --> 08:15.000
and they don't know it is a magic tempest.

08:15.000 --> 08:19.000
From a distance, Prospero is watching the storm.

08:19.000 --> 08:21.000
His magic is working well,

08:21.000 --> 08:24.000
but Ariel's work is not finished.

08:24.000 --> 08:27.000
Prospero has plans for the men,

08:27.000 --> 08:30.000
but first, they must arrive on the island.

08:35.000 --> 08:37.000
Part two.

08:38.000 --> 08:40.000
Good morning, Your Majesty.

08:40.000 --> 08:43.000
Ah, good morning, Antonio.

08:43.000 --> 08:46.000
It's very windy today.

08:46.000 --> 08:48.000
Good morning, Father.

08:48.000 --> 08:50.000
Good morning, Antonio.

08:50.000 --> 08:53.000
Look at the big waves.

08:54.000 --> 08:57.000
There's a big storm today.

08:58.000 --> 08:59.000
Ah!

09:00.000 --> 09:01.000
Look!

09:01.000 --> 09:02.000
Look!

09:17.000 --> 09:19.000
Very good, Ariel.

09:19.000 --> 09:20.000
Yes, sir.

09:20.000 --> 09:22.000
Your magic is very good.

09:22.000 --> 09:25.000
You are very intelligent.

09:25.000 --> 09:28.000
Yes, I know. Thank you, Ariel.

09:28.000 --> 09:32.000
Is the magic finished, sir?

09:32.000 --> 09:34.000
Can I go now?

09:34.000 --> 09:35.000
No, Ariel.

09:35.000 --> 09:38.000
There is more magic for you to do.

09:45.000 --> 09:47.000
Good morning, Antonio.

09:47.000 --> 09:49.000
Are you sleeping?

09:49.000 --> 09:51.000
Oh, good morning, Your Majesty.

09:51.000 --> 09:52.000
What time is it?

09:52.000 --> 09:55.000
It's half past seven, Antonio.

09:55.000 --> 09:57.000
Come on, get up.

09:57.000 --> 09:59.000
Today is not a good day.

09:59.000 --> 10:00.000
Why?

10:00.000 --> 10:01.000
What's the problem?

10:01.000 --> 10:04.000
There is a big storm coming.

10:04.000 --> 10:08.000
The sky is black, and the sea is angry.

10:08.000 --> 10:10.000
And where is your son Ferdinand the Prince?

10:10.000 --> 10:13.000
Ferdinand is reading the book.

10:13.000 --> 10:15.000
And where is Gonzalo?

10:15.000 --> 10:18.000
Gonzalo is an old man.

10:18.000 --> 10:20.000
He is sleeping.

10:21.000 --> 10:23.000
Listen, Your Majesty.

10:23.000 --> 10:25.000
What's that noise?

10:25.000 --> 10:28.000
It's the storm, Antonio.

10:36.000 --> 10:39.000
Listen to the conversation again.

10:40.000 --> 10:42.000
Good morning, Antonio.

10:42.000 --> 10:44.000
Are you sleeping?

10:44.000 --> 10:46.000
Oh, good morning, Your Majesty.

10:46.000 --> 10:47.000
What time is it?

10:47.000 --> 10:50.000
It's half past seven, Antonio.

10:50.000 --> 10:52.000
Come on, get up.

10:52.000 --> 10:54.000
Today is not a good day.

10:54.000 --> 10:55.000
Why?

10:55.000 --> 10:56.000
What's the problem?

10:56.000 --> 10:59.000
There is a big storm coming.

10:59.000 --> 11:03.000
The sky is black, and the sea is angry.

11:03.000 --> 11:06.000
